txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Large filth from the spiders and insects in the central Lone-lands. Bring the filth to Frideric the Elder at Ost Guruth.
'This is proof that you desire to help our people.\n\n'Thank you.'
'Killing the spiders and insects that prey upon my people is a good way to earn my favour. Please remember to gather proof.'
Frideric the Elder at Ost Guruth desires large filth from the insects and spiders found throughout the central and eastern Lone-lands.
Deliver the large filth to Frideric the Elder at Ost Guruth
You accepted a task from Frideric the Elder to acquire large filth from the spiders and insects in the central and eastern Lone-lands. You can find Frideric the Elder within Ost Guruth.
Wanted: Large filth from the spiders and insects in the central Lone-lands.
